{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-2/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"50286e7c-c21c-5d3b-9eeb-0f2207bf1176","excerpt":"개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 기본 세팅을 완료했으면 테일윈드 CSS(Tailwind CSS)를 적용해 보도록 할게요. 이전 포스트에서 세팅한 블로그 디렉터리 위치로 이동해주세요.  1. Tailwind CSS 의존성 설치 그리고 아래 명령어로 테일윈드 CSS…","html":"<p><a href=\"https://whitepaek.com/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-1/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 기본 세팅</a>을 완료했으면 <a href=\"https://tailwindcss.com/docs/guides/gatsby\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">테일윈드 CSS(Tailwind CSS)를 적용</a>해 보도록 할게요.</p>\n<p>이전 포스트에서 세팅한 블로그 디렉터리 위치로 이동해주세요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> ~/Downloads/my-blog-starter/</code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6b212385ce16b2416f7da5bdfbfba8c1/d50e7/move-project-directory.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.45569620253164%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"gatsby-starter-blog 프로젝트 디렉터리 위치로 이동\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/6b212385ce16b2416f7da5bdfbfba8c1/f058b/move-project-directory.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6b212385ce16b2416f7da5bdfbfba8c1/c26ae/move-project-directory.png 158w,\n/static/6b212385ce16b2416f7da5bdfbfba8c1/6bdcf/move-project-directory.png 315w,\n/static/6b212385ce16b2416f7da5bdfbfba8c1/f058b/move-project-directory.png 630w,\n/static/6b212385ce16b2416f7da5bdfbfba8c1/40601/move-project-directory.png 945w,\n/static/6b212385ce16b2416f7da5bdfbfba8c1/78612/move-project-directory.png 1260w,\n/static/6b212385ce16b2416f7da5bdfbfba8c1/d50e7/move-project-directory.png 2280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">gatsby-starter-blog 프로젝트 디렉터리 위치로 이동</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>1. Tailwind CSS 의존성 설치</strong><br>\n그리고 아래 명령어로 테일윈드 CSS 사용에 필요한 의존성을 설치해 주세요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-D</span> tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer gatsby-plugin-postcss</code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/364cc83add1281e5a320fcca01882278/d50e7/dependencies-install.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.45569620253164%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[1] Tailwind CSS 의존성 설치\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/364cc83add1281e5a320fcca01882278/f058b/dependencies-install.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/364cc83add1281e5a320fcca01882278/c26ae/dependencies-install.png 158w,\n/static/364cc83add1281e5a320fcca01882278/6bdcf/dependencies-install.png 315w,\n/static/364cc83add1281e5a320fcca01882278/f058b/dependencies-install.png 630w,\n/static/364cc83add1281e5a320fcca01882278/40601/dependencies-install.png 945w,\n/static/364cc83add1281e5a320fcca01882278/78612/dependencies-install.png 1260w,\n/static/364cc83add1281e5a320fcca01882278/d50e7/dependencies-install.png 2280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[1] Tailwind CSS 의존성 설치</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>2. Tailwind CSS 설정 파일 생성</strong><br>\n의존성 설치가 완료되었으면, 테일윈드 설정 파일을 아래 명령어로 생성해 주세요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ npx tailwindcss init <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-p</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/29206f1f01fa82ea4acd304647293878/d50e7/init-tailwindcss.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.45569620253164%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[2] Tailwind CSS 설정 파일 생성\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/29206f1f01fa82ea4acd304647293878/f058b/init-tailwindcss.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/29206f1f01fa82ea4acd304647293878/c26ae/init-tailwindcss.png 158w,\n/static/29206f1f01fa82ea4acd304647293878/6bdcf/init-tailwindcss.png 315w,\n/static/29206f1f01fa82ea4acd304647293878/f058b/init-tailwindcss.png 630w,\n/static/29206f1f01fa82ea4acd304647293878/40601/init-tailwindcss.png 945w,\n/static/29206f1f01fa82ea4acd304647293878/78612/init-tailwindcss.png 1260w,\n/static/29206f1f01fa82ea4acd304647293878/d50e7/init-tailwindcss.png 2280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[2] Tailwind CSS 설정 파일 생성</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>3. Tailwind CSS 의존성, 설정 파일 세팅 결과 확인</strong><br>\n테일윈드 CSS에 필요한 의존성 설치부터 설정 파일 생성까지 완료했다면,<br>\n<strong>package.json</strong> 파일에 <strong>\"autoprefixer, gatsby-plugin-postcss, postcss, tailwindcss\"</strong> 의존성이 추가되고<br>\n<strong>postcss.config.js</strong> 파일과 <strong>tailwind.config.js</strong> 파일이 생성된걸 볼 수 있어요.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b5ef46a9fd3a20e802eb88f58345cff4/669cd/added-tailwindcss-files.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 73.41772151898735%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[3] Tailwind CSS 의존성, 설정 파일 세팅 결과\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/b5ef46a9fd3a20e802eb88f58345cff4/f058b/added-tailwindcss-files.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b5ef46a9fd3a20e802eb88f58345cff4/c26ae/added-tailwindcss-files.png 158w,\n/static/b5ef46a9fd3a20e802eb88f58345cff4/6bdcf/added-tailwindcss-files.png 315w,\n/static/b5ef46a9fd3a20e802eb88f58345cff4/f058b/added-tailwindcss-files.png 630w,\n/static/b5ef46a9fd3a20e802eb88f58345cff4/40601/added-tailwindcss-files.png 945w,\n/static/b5ef46a9fd3a20e802eb88f58345cff4/78612/added-tailwindcss-files.png 1260w,\n/static/b5ef46a9fd3a20e802eb88f58345cff4/669cd/added-tailwindcss-files.png 3024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[3] Tailwind CSS 의존성, 설정 파일 세팅 결과</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>기본적인 세팅은 완료했고, 이제부터 테일윈드 CSS 사용을 위해 설정을 진행할게요.</p>\n<p><strong>4. PostCSS 플러그인 추가</strong><br>\n<strong>gatsby-config.js</strong> 파일을 열고 plugins 하위에 <strong>gatsby-plugin-postcss</strong>을 추가해주세요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">`gatsby-plugin-postcss`,</code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/aa11639921408a813ad2f15259ddfda6/6c837/added-dependency-postcss.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80.37974683544303%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[4] gatsby-config.js 파일에 PostCSS 플러그인 추가\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/aa11639921408a813ad2f15259ddfda6/f058b/added-dependency-postcss.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aa11639921408a813ad2f15259ddfda6/c26ae/added-dependency-postcss.png 158w,\n/static/aa11639921408a813ad2f15259ddfda6/6bdcf/added-dependency-postcss.png 315w,\n/static/aa11639921408a813ad2f15259ddfda6/f058b/added-dependency-postcss.png 630w,\n/static/aa11639921408a813ad2f15259ddfda6/40601/added-dependency-postcss.png 945w,\n/static/aa11639921408a813ad2f15259ddfda6/78612/added-dependency-postcss.png 1260w,\n/static/aa11639921408a813ad2f15259ddfda6/6c837/added-dependency-postcss.png 2962w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[4] gatsby-config.js 파일에 PostCSS 플러그인 추가</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>5. Tailwind CSS 사용을 위한 경로 설정</strong><br>\n<strong>tailwind.config.js</strong> 파일을 열고 content 하위에 테일윈드 CSS를 적용할 페이지 경로를 추가해 주세요.\n개츠비 블로그의 기본 디렉터리 구조에서는 <strong>\"components, pages, templates\"</strong> 하위에 페이지를 구성하기 때문에 3개의 디렉터리 경로를 추가해 주세요.\n(디렉터리 구조를 변경 또는 추가 한다면 경로를 추가로 설정하면 돼요.)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">\"./src/components/**/*.{js,jsx,ts,tsx}\",\n\"./src/pages/**/*.{js,jsx,ts,tsx}\",\n\"./src/templates/**/*.{js,jsx,ts,tsx}\",</code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6ec7c370901e4d726fb8a282fea9bed2/6c837/added-tailwindcss-direcotry-path.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80.37974683544303%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[5] Tailwind CSS를 적용할 디렉터리 경로 설정\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/6ec7c370901e4d726fb8a282fea9bed2/f058b/added-tailwindcss-direcotry-path.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6ec7c370901e4d726fb8a282fea9bed2/c26ae/added-tailwindcss-direcotry-path.png 158w,\n/static/6ec7c370901e4d726fb8a282fea9bed2/6bdcf/added-tailwindcss-direcotry-path.png 315w,\n/static/6ec7c370901e4d726fb8a282fea9bed2/f058b/added-tailwindcss-direcotry-path.png 630w,\n/static/6ec7c370901e4d726fb8a282fea9bed2/40601/added-tailwindcss-direcotry-path.png 945w,\n/static/6ec7c370901e4d726fb8a282fea9bed2/78612/added-tailwindcss-direcotry-path.png 1260w,\n/static/6ec7c370901e4d726fb8a282fea9bed2/6c837/added-tailwindcss-direcotry-path.png 2962w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[5] Tailwind CSS를 적용할 디렉터리 경로 설정</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>6. global.css 파일 생성</strong><br>\n<strong>src</strong> 디렉터리 하위에 <strong>styles</strong> 디렉터리를 생성하고, <strong>global.css</strong> 파일을 생성해 주세요.\n그리고 파일에 아래 내용을 작성해 주세요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@tailwind</span> base<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@tailwind</span> components<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@tailwind</span> utilities<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/660fa66a1496c934f26e473270f30434/6c837/added-global-css-.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80.37974683544303%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[6] global.css 생성\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/660fa66a1496c934f26e473270f30434/f058b/added-global-css-.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/660fa66a1496c934f26e473270f30434/c26ae/added-global-css-.png 158w,\n/static/660fa66a1496c934f26e473270f30434/6bdcf/added-global-css-.png 315w,\n/static/660fa66a1496c934f26e473270f30434/f058b/added-global-css-.png 630w,\n/static/660fa66a1496c934f26e473270f30434/40601/added-global-css-.png 945w,\n/static/660fa66a1496c934f26e473270f30434/78612/added-global-css-.png 1260w,\n/static/660fa66a1496c934f26e473270f30434/6c837/added-global-css-.png 2962w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[6] global.css 생성</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>7. global.css 파일 설정</strong><br>\n<strong>gatsby-browser.js</strong> 파일에 global.css 파일을 import 해주세요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./src/styles/global.css'</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f0403361cc355d4e96ea8246749f0fa4/6c837/import-global-css.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80.37974683544303%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[7] global.css import 설정\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/f0403361cc355d4e96ea8246749f0fa4/f058b/import-global-css.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f0403361cc355d4e96ea8246749f0fa4/c26ae/import-global-css.png 158w,\n/static/f0403361cc355d4e96ea8246749f0fa4/6bdcf/import-global-css.png 315w,\n/static/f0403361cc355d4e96ea8246749f0fa4/f058b/import-global-css.png 630w,\n/static/f0403361cc355d4e96ea8246749f0fa4/40601/import-global-css.png 945w,\n/static/f0403361cc355d4e96ea8246749f0fa4/78612/import-global-css.png 1260w,\n/static/f0403361cc355d4e96ea8246749f0fa4/6c837/import-global-css.png 2962w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[7] global.css import 설정</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>8. Tailwind CSS 문법 적용</strong><br>\n테일윈드 CSS 사용을 위한 준비 과정이 전부 끝났어요.<br>\n테일윈드 CSS가 잘 적용되는지 확인을 위해 테스트용 페이지를 생성해서 적용해 보도록 할게요.\n저는 pages 디렉터리 하위에 <strong>tailwindcss 디렉터리와 index.js 파일을 생성</strong>하도록 할게요.\n그리고 <a href=\"https://tailwindui.com/components/marketing/feedback/404-pages\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">테일윈드 UI 컴포넌트</a>의 404 Pages 코드를 사용할게요.<br>\n아래 코드를 복사해서 생성한 index.js 파일에 작성해 주세요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">TailwindcssIndex</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>main className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"grid min-h-full place-items-center bg-white px-6 py-24 sm:py-32 lg:px-8\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"text-center\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>p className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"text-base font-semibold text-indigo-600\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token number\">404</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>h1 className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"mt-4 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>Page not found<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>h1<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>p className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"mt-6 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>Sorry<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> we couldn’t find the page you’re looking <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n            <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>a href<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"#\"</span>\n               className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"rounded-md bg-indigo-600 px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-indigo-500 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-600\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>Go\n              back home<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>a<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n            <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>a href<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"#\"</span> className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>Contact support <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>span\n              aria<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>hidden<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"true\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span>rarr<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>span<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>a<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>main<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> TailwindcssIndex</code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2b10441b7041fd2cd5af375240f7055a/000b4/tailwindcss-test.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 82.27848101265823%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[8-1] Tailwind UI의 404 Pages 컴포넌트를 이용한 Tailwind CSS 적용 테스트\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/2b10441b7041fd2cd5af375240f7055a/f058b/tailwindcss-test.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2b10441b7041fd2cd5af375240f7055a/c26ae/tailwindcss-test.png 158w,\n/static/2b10441b7041fd2cd5af375240f7055a/6bdcf/tailwindcss-test.png 315w,\n/static/2b10441b7041fd2cd5af375240f7055a/f058b/tailwindcss-test.png 630w,\n/static/2b10441b7041fd2cd5af375240f7055a/40601/tailwindcss-test.png 945w,\n/static/2b10441b7041fd2cd5af375240f7055a/78612/tailwindcss-test.png 1260w,\n/static/2b10441b7041fd2cd5af375240f7055a/000b4/tailwindcss-test.png 2912w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[8-1] Tailwind UI의 404 Pages 컴포넌트를 이용한 Tailwind CSS 적용 테스트</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>코드 준비가 완료됐으면 개츠비 서버를 실행 후, <code class=\"language-text\">http://localhost:8000/tailwindcss/</code>로 접속하여 404 Pages 컴포넌트가 잘 나오는지 확인해 주세요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> ~/Downloads/my-blog-starter/\n$ gatsby develop</code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0968463af59fddb141f001f7d067d93e/41045/404-pages-compoent.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 67.72151898734178%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[8-2] Tailwind UI 404 Pages 컴포넌트 적용 확인\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/0968463af59fddb141f001f7d067d93e/f058b/404-pages-compoent.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0968463af59fddb141f001f7d067d93e/c26ae/404-pages-compoent.png 158w,\n/static/0968463af59fddb141f001f7d067d93e/6bdcf/404-pages-compoent.png 315w,\n/static/0968463af59fddb141f001f7d067d93e/f058b/404-pages-compoent.png 630w,\n/static/0968463af59fddb141f001f7d067d93e/40601/404-pages-compoent.png 945w,\n/static/0968463af59fddb141f001f7d067d93e/78612/404-pages-compoent.png 1260w,\n/static/0968463af59fddb141f001f7d067d93e/41045/404-pages-compoent.png 2434w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[8-2] Tailwind UI 404 Pages 컴포넌트 적용 확인</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그에 테일윈드 CSS(Tailwind CSS) 적용을 완료했어요!</p>\n<p>테일윈드 CSS 문법은 <a href=\"https://tailwindcss.com/docs/grid-template-columns\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">공식 문서</a>를 통해 확인하고 사용하면 돼요.\n테일윈드 CSS를 사용하기 위해서는 <a href=\"https://whitepaek.com/posts/2024/01/css-vanilla-component-utility/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">CSS 비교 (Vanilla CSS vs CSS Framework)</a> 포스트에서 설명했듯,\n바닐라 CSS(Vanilla CSS) 문법의 기본적인 동작 방식에 대한 이해와 테일윈드 CSS 문법을 학습해야 해요.\n(테일윈드 UI 컴포넌트를 활용하면 학습에 도움이 될 수 있어요.)</p>\n<hr>\n<p>이번 포스트를 끝내기 전에 <strong>style.css</strong> 파일과 <strong>normalize.css</strong> 파일은 어떻게 해야 하는지 궁금하실 거예요.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4d2a481e6bc708c7ed7df109a4890903/000b4/css-files.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 82.27848101265823%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[9] style.css, normalize.css 파일\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/4d2a481e6bc708c7ed7df109a4890903/f058b/css-files.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4d2a481e6bc708c7ed7df109a4890903/c26ae/css-files.png 158w,\n/static/4d2a481e6bc708c7ed7df109a4890903/6bdcf/css-files.png 315w,\n/static/4d2a481e6bc708c7ed7df109a4890903/f058b/css-files.png 630w,\n/static/4d2a481e6bc708c7ed7df109a4890903/40601/css-files.png 945w,\n/static/4d2a481e6bc708c7ed7df109a4890903/78612/css-files.png 1260w,\n/static/4d2a481e6bc708c7ed7df109a4890903/000b4/css-files.png 2912w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[9] style.css, normalize.css 파일</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>테일윈드 CSS만 사용하실 거라면 style.css, normalize.css 파일을 삭제하고 gatsby-browser.js 파일에서 2개의 import를 제거하세요.\n테일윈드 CSS 문법을 커스텀에서 사용하고 싶으면 <a href=\"https://tailwindcss.com/docs/adding-custom-styles\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">공식 문서</a>를 참고해서 <strong>tailwind.config.js 파일에 설정</strong>하면 돼요.\n그리고 클래스(class)를 직접 정의해서 사용하고 싶다면 global.css 파일에 추가하거나 또는 css 파일을 생성하여 작성 후 gatsby-browser.js 파일에 import 하면 돼요.</p>\n<p>테일윈드 CSS를 사용하지 않고 본인이 직접 CSS를 작성하여 디자인하고 싶다면, 이번 포스트 설정은 따라 하지 않고 style.css 파일에 직접 코드를 작성해서 사용하면 돼요.</p>\n<p>이상으로 <strong>\"개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 2 - Tailwind CSS 적용\"</strong> 포스트는 끝낼게요!</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 2 - Tailwind CSS 적용","description":null,"createdAt":"2024-01-18","editedAt":"2024-01-18"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 1 - 기본 세팅"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-3/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 3 - Pagination 적용"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"50286e7c-c21c-5d3b-9eeb-0f2207bf1176","previousPostId":"b10c0155-102d-5f8e-9f2a-d84671d49cee","nextPostId":"75b54429-d5c4-5127-a853-b9f982a6d2c8"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3764592887"],"slicesMap":{}}